title: Ashwin
userTestimonialDetail: I am  really thankful to all the members of HHC team who are dedicated to make your trek success without any difficulties. Moreover,The hike was as much about learning the geology, flora, fauna, and “leave no trace” principles as it was about seeing the Himalayas Brahmataal trek with HHC was, hands down, THE MOST MAGNIFICENT experience i ever had!
